name: Purah - Tears of the Kingdom/Hyrule Warriors (Character)
description:
This is a LORA of the character Purah from Nintendo's Tears of the Kingdom and Omega Force's Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity. This was trained on Anything4.5 with Clip Skip 2.

To prompt this character from ToTK, enter "<lora:Purahv2:0.7>purah_totk, gold hair ornament, hair stick, sleeveless shirt, white jacket, red glasses, black gloves, red pantyhose, high heels," to prompt her Hyrule Warriors appearance, enter "<lora:Purahv2:0.7>purah_hw, multicolored hair, robe, black skirt, glasses on head, bridal gauntlets". This lora was also trained on ingame 3D model images from the games, to add in the 3D aesthetic, prompt "3D model".

This is an update to an old request from a discord user. Felt the need to update this considering ToTK's release, and the old v1 was super outdated. This version is very customizable!
